.Xr pccard 4 ,
.Xr sa 4 ,
.Xr scsi 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver has been developed for
.Nx Ns / Ns Tn pc98
and ported for
.Fx .
It first appeared in
.Fx 3.4
with PAO3 and merged in
.Fx 4.2 .
